average weight of X <-- list X of persons:
    count = 0
    sum = 0
    while X != ():
        next count = count + 1
	next sum = sum + the weight of (first X)
	next X = rest X
    if count == 0:
        value = error ``Cannot average 0 things.''
    else:
        value = sum / count
